{
  "stem": "13469.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because in 1942, they, with all the other rules and regulations that we had, we weren't allowed to do this, that, and we weren't allowed to do anything, more or less.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a curfew [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were not allowed out after 8 o'clock in the evening-- [INAUDIBLE] before-- between 8 o'clock in the evening, 6 o'clock in the morning, we were not allowed outside our houses.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all those kinds of things they could enforce very easily, because we had the star and the identity card with a J.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you walked around without the star, you were liable to be instantly sent to a concentration camp or various punishments.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You-- you were threatened, if you did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we were always threatened with being sent to-- to the East or sent away to camps kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not sure whether they were described as concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When-- when we heard that term first, I can't really remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it sounded bad, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a bad thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were basically, again, sticking to the rules.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, my father wouldn't do anything that wasn't according to the rules.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So if you had to wear the star, we wore the star.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, we-- an interesting thing was that, by that time, when we were in Amsterdam and my father worked for the Judenrat, my father then recognized the benefit of Eve being British.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know whether he recognized it earlier where this was always planned, but we found out on our list of documents-- well, we haven't actually found the actual documents, but we have this handwritten list of documents, which maybe we gave to somebody and we never got back.",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
